&lt;p&gt;Management Accountant - Band 6 (Indicative Banding – Pending Agenda for Change evaluation) Fixed Term / secondment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;South Sefton Clinical Commissioning Group has 30 constituent practices and serves a population of around 155,000 with a budget of approximately £290 million. Southport and Formby Clinical Commissioning Group has 18 constituent practices and serves a population of around 126,000 with a budget of approximately £220 million. Both CCGs have four localities, with designated clinical and managerial leadership, to ensure that the CCG improves the health and wellbeing of local people by commissioning services that are better tailored to their specific communities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Southport and Formby CCG and South Sefton CCG operate a joint management structure to support both organisations in a streamlined and cost-effective way. The CCGs wish to appoint to the post of Management Accountant for a fixed term of up to 9 months.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post will be key in supporting the CCG’s to deliver statutory financial duties whilst delivering their vision to improve health outcomes and reduce inequalities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Management Accountant will support both Clinical Commissioning Groups in Sefton with financial management support.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Play a key role in supporting the CCG management team and board with financial reporting information, costing advice, business case preparation as well as the month end financial process.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post will also play a key role in supporting the Finance Department in all aspects of financial management and financial planning for the CCG.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will provide support to the CCG in relation to the CCG’s Running Cost and Primary Care cost centres and associated processes&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you wish to discuss this post informally please contact Jason Morris jason.morris@southseftonccg.nhs.uk in the first instance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details please contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jason Morris&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contract Accountant&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address:   jason.morris@southseftonccg.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number   0151 3178456&lt;/p&gt;
